data.description: Beautifully maintained log home near Grand Marais. This custom-built log home boasts character and quality beyond measure - custom made doors, handcrafted bathroom vanity, tigerwood flooring, and hand-picked local logs just to name a few. The home features 2 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, vaulted ceiling, custom kitchen dining table, countertop and cabinets, panoramic picture windows, basement walkout, main floor bathroom with bubble tub, bedroom balcony and a two-stall detached garage with a beautiful pine tongue and groove heated bonus room. The wooded retreat is nestled on 2.88 acres of tall pines surrounded by The Superior National Forest. Enjoy the breathtaking views of wildlife, sunrises, sunsets and the spectacular Northern Lights from the spacious back deck. This home sits just minutes away from the Superior Hiking Trail and Cascade River waterfalls. Schedule your personal showing today to see for yourself!
